title: Behind Blue Skies HDTV STORM
description:
Title: Behind Blue Skies HDTV STORM

Release: HDTV

Genre: Drama 

Director: Hannes Holm

Cast: Peter Dalle, Josefin Ljungman, Amanda Ooms

Country: Sweden

Subtitles: Bulgarian, Albanian, Macedonian, Serbian, Croatian

Storyline:

Coming of age film that takes place in the swedish archipelago during 70's about young Martin(played by Bill Skarsgard)who gets a summer job working at a hotel. The hotel manager Gosta(played by Peter Dalle) takes a liking to young Martin, takes him around while doing some very shady business deals outside of his hotel manager job.
